  "lyrics": {
    "v1": "Almighty God, Your Word is cast Like seed into the ground; Now let the dew of Heav&#39;n descend, And righteous fruits abound.",
    "v2": "Let not the foe of Christ and man This holy seed remove, But give it root in ev&#39;ry heart To bring forth fruits of love.",
    "v3": "Let not the world&#39;s deceitful cares The rising plant destroy. But let it yield a hundredfold The fruits of peace and joy.",
    "v4": "Nor let Your Word so kindly sent To raise us to Your throne Return to You, and sadly tell That we reject Your Son.",
    "v5": "Oft as the precious seed is sown, Your quick&#39;ning grace bestow, That all whose souls the truth receive, Its saving power may know."
  },
